WEBVTT

00:00:27.071 --> 00:00:30.508
na korišćenju vrhunskih
molekularnih tehnika,

00:00:30.508 --> 00:00:33.120
zasnovane na DNK i RNK metodama

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:36.559
da posmatram mikrobne populacije
u biološkim reaktorima,

00:00:36.559 --> 00:00:38.922
i da opet unapredim ove sisteme.

00:00:38.922 --> 00:00:40.171
I tokom godina,

00:00:40.171 --> 00:00:44.423
razvila se bolesna opsesija
prema toaletima,

00:00:44.423 --> 00:00:47.415
i znao sam da se uvučem u toalet

00:00:47.415 --> 00:00:49.218
i da ponesem telefon

00:00:49.218 --> 00:00:51.566
širom sveta.

00:00:51.566 --> 00:00:53.790
Ali usput sam naučio

00:00:53.790 --> 00:00:56.332
da ne postoji samo ta tehnička strana,

00:00:56.332 --> 00:01:00.510
već i takozvana kultura sranja.